Subject: Apple Website - Non Persistent Cross Site
	Scripting Vulnerability

Title:
======
Apple Website - Non Persistent Cross Site Vulnerability


Date:
=====
2011-10-07


References:
===========
http://www.vulnerability-lab.com/get_content.php?id=289


VL-ID:
=====
289


Introduction:
=============
